    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for earthenware having a white, shiny, opaque glaze comprising lead with tin oxide. On this white background are typically brightly colored patterns, scenes, or other decoration.</Note_Text>
